00:38:44,340 --> 00:38:45,870
got the searing karmic fire

844
00:38:46,000 --> 00:38:47,810
that they gathered

845
00:38:47,830 --> 00:38:50,200
tens of millions of evil soldiers to wipe out the Southwest Seven States

846
00:38:50,200 --> 00:38:51,600
and established Nanyin.

847
00:38:52,330 --> 00:38:53,520
Is it a legend?

848
00:38:53,680 --> 00:38:54,810
That's impossible.

849
00:38:54,880 --> 00:38:55,880
My grandfather

850
00:38:55,910 --> 00:38:57,980
never writes things without evidence down.

851
00:38:57,980 --> 00:38:58,820
Let me think.

852
00:38:59,930 --> 00:39:01,130
Searing karmic fire.

853
00:39:01,690 --> 00:39:03,550
My grandfather described it

854
00:39:04,120 --> 00:39:05,650
as not only the sorcery which didn't belong to mortals

855
00:39:05,650 --> 00:39:07,250
but also the root of all evil.

856
00:39:07,480 --> 00:39:08,880
This thing is quite evil.

857
00:39:09,290 --> 00:39:10,500
But in the past hundred years,

858
00:39:10,500 --> 00:39:11,840
no one has mentioned it.

859
00:39:12,180 --> 00:39:13,750
I thought they had already disappeared.

860
00:39:13,750 --> 00:39:15,360
The Nanyin people respect grass and trees.

861
00:39:15,360 --> 00:39:16,980
The searing karmic fire is being held at the top.

862
00:39:16,980 --> 00:39:17,820
There's "fire" in its name.

863
00:39:17,820 --> 00:39:19,240
Fire burns grass and trees.

864
00:39:19,240 --> 00:39:22,640
I guess the Nanyin people not only respect it but also fear it.

865
00:39:22,660 --> 00:39:25,120
The vessel with the searing karmic fire in it

866
00:39:26,530 --> 00:39:27,990
should be the Rama Vessel.

867
00:39:28,860 --> 00:39:31,170
Why does the vessel have such a strange name?

868
00:39:31,170 --> 00:39:32,320
This should be right.

869
00:39:32,320 --> 00:39:34,710
The Rama Vessel was made in the Blood Realm Tianqiao Palace a few hundred years ago.

870
00:39:34,710 --> 00:39:36,580
It has mechanisms in it, so it is extremely hard to open.

871
00:39:36,580 --> 00:39:37,940
Only by using four pieces of Rama Heavenly Ice as a key

872
00:39:37,940 --> 00:39:39,060
can it be opened.

873
00:39:39,510 --> 00:39:40,330
My aunt said

874
00:39:40,640 --> 00:39:42,080
Jin Mantang's ice shard

875
00:39:42,450 --> 00:39:43,410
is a kind of key.

876
00:39:43,960 --> 00:39:46,420
Could the ice shard be the Rama Heavenly Ice?

877
00:39:46,860 --> 00:39:48,060
So the reason why those people

878
00:39:48,060 --> 00:39:50,130
want to collect four pieces of Rama Heavenly Ice

879
00:39:50,130 --> 00:39:51,800
is that they want to open the Rama Vessel.

880
00:39:51,800 --> 00:39:53,460
There were four Nanyin people

881
00:39:54,190 --> 00:39:55,020
who came to Central Plains.

882
00:39:55,020 --> 00:39:56,480
Each of them had one piece.

883
00:39:57,580 --> 00:40:00,590
It seems that if we find the remaining three descendants

884
00:40:00,590 --> 00:40:02,290
and the other three ice shards,

885
00:40:02,290 --> 00:40:03,570
we can find the person

886
00:40:03,750 --> 00:40:05,310
who's hidden in the dark.

887
00:40:05,860 --> 00:40:07,300
If the searing karmic fire

888
00:40:07,300 --> 00:40:08,830
is really something scary,

889
00:40:09,060 --> 00:40:10,770
we must inform the Baichuan Court immediately.

890
00:40:10,770 --> 00:40:11,250
No.

891
00:40:11,420 --> 00:40:11,980
Why?

892
00:40:12,670 --> 00:40:13,530
Think about it.

893
00:40:13,820 --> 00:40:15,940
Yipin Tomb and Yuanbao Villa.

894
00:40:15,940 --> 00:40:17,780
Every time when we sent the messages

895
00:40:17,780 --> 00:40:19,230
to the Baichuan Court before,

896
00:40:19,230 --> 00:40:21,710
we would be attacked.

897
00:40:22,200 --> 00:40:22,860
You suspect

898
00:40:23,780 --> 00:40:25,300
there's a spy in the Baichuan Court?

899
00:40:25,300 --> 00:40:25,860
Yes.

900
00:40:26,580 --> 00:40:28,500
So we have to look for the remaining three people

901
00:40:28,500 --> 00:40:29,740
ourselves.

902
00:40:30,230 --> 00:40:32,110
But there are three people.

903
00:40:32,670 --> 00:40:33,870
We only know one name.

904
00:40:34,250 --> 00:40:36,050
How can we investigate the rest?

905
00:40:37,660 --> 00:40:38,400
Miss Zhiyu.

906
00:40:38,980 --> 00:40:39,980
Does Jin Mantang

907
00:40:40,130 --> 00:40:42,220
have any friends who he meets regularly?

908
00:40:42,220 --> 00:40:44,660
Not many.

909
00:40:45,100 --> 00:40:47,300
But he goes out for a few days every fall.

910
00:40:47,880 --> 00:40:49,540
He said he went out for a feast.

911
00:40:49,720 --> 00:40:50,830
Feasts in fall?

912
00:40:52,540 --> 00:40:54,000
Could it be Mountains Red?

913
00:40:54,080 --> 00:40:56,180
"Mountains Red" was written on the invitations.

914
00:40:56,180 --> 00:40:57,440
What is Mountains Red?

915
00:40:57,620 --> 00:40:59,620
Aren't you the granddaughter of the All-Knowing?

916
00:40:59,620 --> 00:41:01,550
You don't even know Mountains Red?

917
00:41:02,350 --> 00:41:03,670
No one knows play

918
00:41:03,760 --> 00:41:05,490
better than you.

919
00:41:05,620 --> 00:41:06,750
-Right?
-Of course.

920
00:41:07,350 --> 00:41:09,080
Let me teach you something new.

921
00:41:09,550 --> 00:41:11,180
Every year when the color of maple leaves becomes red,

922
00:41:11,180 --> 00:41:12,590
Yu Louchun

923
00:41:12,620 --> 00:41:14,780
invites six strange people to the banquet.

924
00:41:14,780 --> 00:41:16,580
This is called "Mountains Red".

925
00:41:16,670 --> 00:41:17,580
Coincidentally,

926
00:41:17,580 --> 00:41:19,520
Yu Louchun is also fabulously rich.

927
00:41:19,520 --> 00:41:20,300
He doesn't go out of his house

928
00:41:20,300 --> 00:41:21,630
and lives in seclusion.

929
00:41:21,630 --> 00:41:23,750
He's very similar to Jin Mantang.

930
00:41:24,010 --> 00:41:26,460
Since we're suspicious of Yu Louchun the most,

931
00:41:26,460 --> 00:41:27,300
why don't we

932
00:41:28,250 --> 00:41:29,450
go and see him?

933
00:41:29,860 --> 00:41:30,480
Yu Louchun is not a person

934
00:41:30,480 --> 00:41:32,180
who you can see when you want to.

935
00:41:32,180 --> 00:41:32,940
Although

936
00:41:32,940 --> 00:41:34,820
he holds Mountains Red every year,

937
00:41:34,820 --> 00:41:35,660
so far,

938
00:41:36,180 --> 00:41:37,340
no one knows

939
00:41:37,500 --> 00:41:38,840
where he lives.

940
00:41:39,260 --> 00:41:40,140
Only guests who are invited

941
00:41:40,140 --> 00:41:41,290
can see him.

942
00:41:41,470 --> 00:41:43,960
I wonder if he needs a doctor.

943
00:41:44,210 --> 00:41:45,850
He didn't say he's sickly.

944
00:41:46,300 --> 00:41:47,500
Let me put it this way.

945
00:41:47,740 --> 00:41:48,940
If you want to see him,

946
00:41:49,250 --> 00:41:51,220
you must become the most famous strange people

947
00:41:51,220 --> 00:41:52,810
in the martial arts world this year.

948
00:41:52,810 --> 00:41:54,970
If you want to be invited, you have to be strange.

949
00:41:54,970 --> 00:41:56,170
We have to be strange?

950
00:41:59,380 --> 00:42:00,650
Among us,

951
00:42:00,980 --> 00:42:01,980
isn't Fei

952
00:42:02,300 --> 00:42:03,460
the strangest person?

953
00:42:03,460 --> 00:42:05,720
How about we ask him to perform on the street

954
00:42:05,720 --> 00:42:06,980
to attract Yu Louchun?

955
00:42:10,170 --> 00:42:11,070
Don't bother.

956
00:42:11,430 --> 00:42:12,550
Just kill them all.

957
00:42:15,460 --> 00:42:16,340
Don't be afraid.

958
00:42:16,340 --> 00:42:18,620
He likes to talk nonsense.

959
00:42:19,710 --> 00:42:21,970
It seems that if we want to see Yu Louchun,

960
00:42:22,150 --> 00:42:24,350
I have to take matters into my own hands.

961
00:42:30,460 --> 00:42:31,430
Are you here

962
00:42:31,890 --> 00:42:33,520
for the rumors in the martial arts world

963
00:42:33,520 --> 00:42:35,260
which have a negative effect on the Sigu Sect?

964
00:42:35,260 --> 00:42:35,820
Yes.

965
00:42:36,910 --> 00:42:38,830
I wonder who spread the rumor

966
00:42:39,140 --> 00:42:42,280
that Second Sect Leader Shan died because of Sect Leader Li.

967
00:42:42,280 --> 00:42:43,760
The nonsense

968
00:42:43,930 --> 00:42:45,490
is slanderous.

969
00:42:46,540 --> 00:42:47,160
Actually,

970
00:42:47,900 --> 00:42:49,500
I've heard a little about it.

971
00:42:49,980 --> 00:42:51,460
The Baichuan Court sent me here today

972
00:42:51,460 --> 00:42:52,860
to discuss this with you.

973
00:42:53,360 --> 00:42:55,000
What are you going to do?

974
00:42:58,660 --> 00:42:59,390
I've decided

975
00:43:00,500 --> 00:43:02,050
to hold the Sigu Tea Party.

976
00:43:03,090 --> 00:43:05,290
The first aim is to invite our friends in the martial arts world

977
00:43:05,290 --> 00:43:06,850
and let the former subordinates come back.

978
00:43:06,850 --> 00:43:08,320
The second aim is to quash the rumor

979
00:43:08,320 --> 00:43:09,330
and ask everyone to be united.

980
00:43:09,330 --> 00:43:11,720
The Sigu Tea Party is Sect Leader Li's private tea party.

981
00:43:11,720 --> 00:43:12,920
Who are you to hold it?

982
00:43:14,500 --> 00:43:16,630
The word "Sigu" in the "Sigu Tea Party"

983
00:43:17,020 --> 00:43:19,250
refers to the Sigu Sect, not Li Xiangyi.

984
00:43:19,580 --> 00:43:20,270
And now,

985
00:43:20,970 --> 00:43:22,970
I'm the sect leader of the Sigu Sect.

986
00:43:22,980 --> 00:43:25,170
Can't you just quash it in person?

987
00:43:25,920 --> 00:43:28,980
Why do you want to invite so many people to talk about it?

988
00:43:29,200 --> 00:43:30,300
Rumors are like water.

989
00:43:30,300 --> 00:43:31,980
It's better to give them rational explanation than stop the spread.

990
00:43:31,980 --> 00:43:34,700
If Sect Leader Li knows his tea party is used to solve the crisis of the Sigu Sect,

991
00:43:34,700 --> 00:43:36,460
he'll be happy.

992
00:43:48,590 --> 00:43:49,120
Wanmian.

993
00:43:50,380 --> 00:43:52,030
I wanted to give you a surprise.

994
00:43:52,030 --> 00:43:53,540
I didn't expect you to find it in advance.

995
00:43:53,540 --> 00:43:54,830
All the flowers in the garden

996
00:43:54,830 --> 00:43:55,830
were chosen by me.

997
00:43:55,970 --> 00:43:56,660
Do you like them?

998
00:43:56,660 --> 00:43:57,150
Zijin.

999
00:43:57,980 --> 00:43:59,490
Did you hear the rumors

1000
00:43:59,900 --> 00:44:00,900
about Li Xiangyi?

1001
00:44:03,290 --> 00:44:04,730
They're just rumors.

1002
00:44:05,340 --> 00:44:05,920
But

1003
00:44:06,420 --> 00:44:07,300
you always

1004
00:44:08,060 --> 00:44:09,500
pay extra attention about things about him.

1005
00:44:09,500 --> 00:44:10,630
I've investigated.

1006
00:44:11,260 --> 00:44:13,020
Those rumors were spread on purpose.

